## TL;DR

This repo IS a [Hermes](https://hermes-agent.nousresearch.com/) agent — a Telegram-native librarian bot bound to exactly one Obsidian vault. Messages arrive on Telegram, a deterministic Python hook writes them to the vault's `raw/inbox/` before any LLM runs, then the agent replies conversationally via ChatGPT. Downstream wiki classification is done separately by Claude Code in `{{OPS_REPO}}`, on a schedule.

The repo is also `HERMES_HOME` — Hermes runtime files (sessions, memories, gateway state, SQLite) live here but are gitignored. What's tracked is the agent's PERSONALITY (`SOUL.md`), CONFIG (`config.yaml`), HOOKS, SKILLS, and start script.

**One sentence:** *Telegram message in -> Python hook deterministically writes to `{{VAULT_NAME}}/raw/inbox/` -> ChatGPT replies -> Claude (in `{{OPS_REPO}}`) classifies on a schedule.*

