## Setup (one-time, fresh Mac)

```bash
cd {{LOCAL_ROOT}}/agents/{{AGENT_NAME}}

# 1. Restore secrets from your password manager
cp .env.example .env          # then fill in the values
cp auth.json.example auth.json # then log in with: hermes auth login openai-codex
chmod 600 .env auth.json

# 2. Verify Hermes is installed
hermes --version              # v0.10+

# 3. Test boot (Ctrl-C to stop)
HERMES_HOME=$(pwd) ./scripts/start.sh

# 4. Register with launchd (or skip if {{OPS_REPO}} already did this)
ln -sf {{LOCAL_ROOT}}/{{OPS_REPO}}/launchd/com.alexmind.librarian.{{AGENT_NAME}}.plist \
       ~/Library/LaunchAgents/
launchctl load -w ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.alexmind.librarian.{{AGENT_NAME}}.plist

# 5. Smoke test — message the bot on Telegram, expect a reply within 30s
```

